Namaz, in the form of 2 rakat, in each rak’at, after reciting of <Surah Fateha>, recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 3 times. After namaz, recite the following 70 times…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "100 Rak’at Namaz, 2x2 rakat kar ke, har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 3 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe. Namaz ke baad har ek zikr 70 martaba padhe…", "UrduDescription": "سید ؒنے فرمایا : ۱۰۰ رکعت نماز ہے،جو اس رات پڑھی جاتی ہے اس کی ہر رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۳ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے اور نماز سے فارغ ہونے کے بعد ہر یاک ذکر کو ۷۰ مرتبہ کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": nu